# CLAUDE.md Example for code-ltm

Copy this template to your project's `CLAUDE.md` file and customize it.
This teaches Claude (and other AI agents) how to use code-ltm effectively in your project.

The hybrid pattern below combines **passive context** (critical knowledge embedded directly) with **active retrieval** (tools for deeper exploration). This approach ensures agents always have the most important knowledge without needing to decide to search for it.

---

